# Story 1.4: Implement Fastify API Skeleton

## Story Metadata
- **Epic:** 1 - Project Foundation & Infrastructure
- **Status:** done
- **Implemented:** 2025-12-28
- **Session:** SESSION-003

## User Story
As a **developer**,
I want **a Fastify API server with routes per module**,
So that **the frontend can fetch data and trigger solver**.

## Acceptance Criteria

| AC | Criteria | Status |
|----|----------|--------|
| AC1 | Fastify server starts on port 3001 | PASS |
| AC2 | Routes exist for all modules | PASS |
| AC3 | CORS configured for frontend | PASS |
| AC4 | Health check endpoint works | PASS |

## Implementation Details

### Files Created
- `apps/api/src/index.ts` - Main Fastify server
- `apps/api/src/routes/dashboard.ts` - KPI endpoints
- `apps/api/src/routes/fleet.ts` - Fleet/train endpoints
- `apps/api/src/routes/allocation.ts` - Allocation endpoints
- `apps/api/src/routes/maintenance.ts` - Maintenance endpoints
- `apps/api/src/routes/simulation.ts` - Simulation endpoints

### API Endpoints Implemented
| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | /api/health | Health check |
| GET | /api/dashboard/kpis | Fleet KPIs |
| GET | /api/dashboard/alerts | Maintenance alerts |
| GET | /api/fleet/trains | Train list |
| GET | /api/fleet/depots | Depot list |
| GET | /api/allocation/services | Pending services |
| POST | /api/allocation/recommend | Get recommendations |
| POST | /api/allocation/assign | Assign train |
| GET | /api/maintenance/gantt | Gantt data |
| GET | /api/maintenance/depot-capacity | Capacity data |
| POST | /api/simulation/run | Run simulation |

### Technical Decisions
- Fastify for performance (faster than Express)
- Route-level caching with Redis
- Request validation with Zod schemas

## Dev Notes
API skeleton provides foundation for all frontend features.
Each route module corresponds to a UI section.

